WEBVTT

00:05.483 --> 00:08.000
Bad news is everywhere.


00:11.157 --> 00:15.000
You might sometimes wonder 
if there’s any good news.


00:17.158 --> 00:22.581
The Bible contains 
good news of something better.


00:22.582 --> 00:24.669
It can help you to have 


00:24.668 --> 00:27.431
a happy family life, 


00:27.432 --> 00:30.769
true friendships, 


00:30.768 --> 00:34.471
inner peace.


00:34.472 --> 00:36.390
It answers life’s big questions, 


00:36.390 --> 00:39.727
such as: 
What is the meaning of life? 


00:39.727 --> 00:42.774
Is God to blame for our suffering? 


00:42.773 --> 00:45.356
What happens when you die?


00:45.357 --> 00:49.152
Would you like to learn more 
about the good news?


00:49.152 --> 00:51.655
Read lesson 1 in the brochure 


00:51.655 --> 00:53.948
Good News From God! 


00:53.948 --> 00:56.951
You can download it 
free of charge from jw.org, 


00:56.952 --> 01:06.817
or you can obtain a copy 
from any of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

